#note cbb: This is a tough rack!

jd: I saw matinee but never really considered wartime or wireman. at the time I figured that with a board that was wide open I needed to play somethin fishy, and so my choice was between AW or MAW. in retrospect, though, I like playing long here. There are two blanks out still (OOT is tough to evaluate, because he could have a blank there, and I think I put him on one at the time). wartime makes it considerably harder for him to bingo if he has a fishy leave, but if he does bingo I still have some lanes.
